OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1779833501
OL,3,CNotts County secure promotion after
OL,4,Cbeating Salford 3-0 at Wembley
OL,6,FDespite punishing temperatures around
OL,7,F37C, Notts County secured promotion to
OL,8,FLeague One after thoroughly beating
OL,9,FSalford 3-0 in the League Two play-off
OL,10,Ffinal at Wembley.
OL,12,FIt's the Magpie's first return to the
OL,13,Fthird tier of England football since
OL,14,F2015.
OL,16,FCounty made it to the final after
OL,17,Fbeating Chesterfield 1-0 on aggregate
OL,18,Fin the semi-final.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
