OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1779833501
OL,3,CNotts County secure promotion after
OL,4,Cbeating Salford 3-0 at Wembley
OL,6,FThey've been in League Two since their
OL,7,Fpromotion in 2023, when they beat
OL,8,FChesterfield 4-3 on a penalty shootout
OL,9,Fin the National League playoff final.
OL,11,FBoth sides made cagey starts but it
OL,12,Fwas County who dominated possession
OL,13,Fand created the game's first chance.
OL,15,FJones, having twice used his skills to
OL,16,Fbeat a Salford challenger, crossed
OL,17,Ffrom the left but Jatta's header from
OL,18,F12 yards was too high.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
