PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1779833501
OL,3,CNotts County secure promotion after
OL,4,Cbeating Salford 3-0 at Wembley
OL,6,FAfter a goalless first half hour,
OL,7,FAlassana Jatta netted the ball in the
OL,8,Fbottom corner in the 32nd minute.
OL,10,FMore than 20,000 Magpies supporters
OL,11,Froared their appreciation of The
OL,12,FGambia forward's 17th goal of the
OL,13,Fseason.
OL,15,FLucas Ness then doubled the lead for
OL,16,FNotts - leaving them 2-0 up at the end
OL,17,Fof the first half.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
